# plan/facts/19-cheapcode-current-state-anchor.bn
#
# Honest snapshot of cheapcode's CURRENT empirical position relative
# to the goal "better and more intelligent general agent for human
# tasks." Per atom 0007 anti-fab + atom 0013 calibration-as-credential:
# state what we have, not what we wish.

# ============================================================
# C1: cheapcode is an opencode fork (architectural inheritance)
# ============================================================
# opencode (sst/opencode) is a working production agent harness with
# multi-step tool dispatch, file edit, bash exec, web fetch, MCP. It
# was already adopted by aapi project before cheapcode forked. Therefore
# cheapcode INHERITS a working agent harness — the question for the
# goal is what substrate enhancements compose with the harness, not
# whether to build a harness.
lemma cheapcode_inherits_working_opencode_agent_harness_no_harness_build_required_l1
  proves True
  by audit aapi-project-uses-opencode-pre-cheapcode-fork-2026-05-03

# ============================================================
# C2: substrate primitives implemented and unit-tested
# ============================================================
# Per facts/13 + M3.x history, cheapcode has implemented:
#   - cross-witness voter v0 (cheap × 2 → escalate to smart_C → 2-of-3)
#   - cheapcode-witness v1x panel-of-experts (cheap × 2 + frontier-d Sonnet 4.6 + synthesizer gpt-5-mini)
#   - tier resolution + provider shape (Vercel AI SDK v3 ProviderV2)
#   - living conversion-factor estimator (median+IQR, multi-dim filter)
#   - atom 0007 anti-fab synthesizer guard (catches contradictions)
# All primitives have unit-test coverage per mizaj 18 burhan-backed TDD.
lemma cheapcode_substrate_primitives_voter_v1x_estimator_anti_fab_implemented_and_unit_tested_l1
  proves True
  by audit cheapcode-src-tests-pass-m3-37-m3-38-anchor

# ============================================================
# C3: empirical evidence on substrate primitives
# ============================================================
# Paired evidence accumulated through M3.x:
#   - M3.23 AIME N=3: 1 win (disphenoid), 1 tie, 1 both-fail
#   - M3.28 v1x dogfood: synthesis-quality lift (qualitative)
#   - M3.36 SWE-bench Verified diagnose N=2: 6/6 PERFECT at $0.094
#   - M3.39 mixed-shape N=3: 3/3=3/3 tied, voter 11.7× cheaper
#   - M3.40 hard-tasks N=3: 3/3=3/3 tied, voter 7.3× cheaper
# Aggregate: N=12 paired, 1 voter-win, 0 voter-loss, 9 ties, 1 both-fail.
# Cost-dominance ~7-12× cheaper across all paired tests (sahih band).
lemma cheapcode_aggregate_n_12_paired_1_win_0_loss_9_ties_1_both_fail_voter_7_to_12x_cheaper_l1
  proves True
  by audit cheapcode-runs-m3-23-m3-28-m3-36-m3-39-m3-40-aggregate-2026-05-03

# ============================================================
# C4: GAP — measurement-zero on canonical practical-task corpora
# ============================================================
# Per facts/16 4 canonical corpora (SWE-bench full / METR HCAST / GAIA
# / OSWorld), cheapcode has measured:
#   - SWE-bench Verified DIAGNOSE-only on N=2 (M3.36, 6/6)
#   - SWE-bench Verified FULL agent loop: 0 measurements
#   - METR HCAST / RE-Bench: 0 measurements
#   - GAIA: 0 measurements
#   - OSWorld: 0 measurements
# This is the LOAD-BEARING GAP between cheapcode's current state and
# the goal. Per atom 0007 anti-fab, claiming "better general agent for
# human tasks" without measurement on these corpora = fabrication.
lemma cheapcode_zero_measurements_on_3_of_4_canonical_corpora_plus_partial_swe_diagnose_only_l1
  proves True
  by audit cheapcode-runs-history-vs-facts-16-corpora-2026-05-03

# ============================================================
# C5: cost-dominance is sahih, correctness-lift is sub-floor
# ============================================================
# Per PLAN.bn SECTION KK + JJ + MM:
#   - cheapcode_decisively_cheaper_than_frontier_on_hard_reasoning: sahih @0.88
#   - cheapcode_at_least_as_correct_as_frontier_on_hard_reasoning: sub-floor @0.80
#   - cheapcode_strictly_more_correct_than_frontier_at_high_rate: daif @0.20 (atom 0015 fired)
#   - voter_much_more_intelligent_on_most_practical_hard_problems: sub-floor @0.55 (M3.43 pre-reg)
# Composed: claim graph supports "AT-LEAST-AS-INTELLIGENT, DECISIVELY
# CHEAPER, FASTER on average" but NOT YET "MUCH MORE INTELLIGENT."
lemma cheapcode_current_claim_graph_at_least_as_correct_decisively_cheaper_not_yet_much_more_intelligent_l1
  proves True
  by audit plan-bn-section-kk-jj-mm-aggregate-2026-05-03
